BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-KlUCS3ER6VvH2W9Ma4g25A">Nguyễn Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-h%C3%A0nh-h%E1%BA%A1t-L%E1%BB%87-s%C6%A1n-ng%E1%BB%99-th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-L%C3%AA-B%C3%ADnh-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-vinh-quy-chi%C3%AAu-du/poem-RYbYU9OZtZjPzukAxJiNbQ">Nhâm Tuất đông hành hạt Lệ sơn ngộ thị độc Lê Bính tiên sinh vinh quy chiêu du - 壬戌冬行轄荔山晤侍讀黎柄先生榮歸招遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-nghi%E1%BB%85n/poem-pFBTTBKCsYJmNWqd2-Mqyw">Thạch nghiễn - 石硯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-hi%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-ToWsywZw7IcPr2fYqiX3Bg">Tống Lý hiệu thư nhị thập lục vận - 送李校書二十六韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-C%E1%BA%A3nh/Tr%E1%BB%AB-d%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-t%C3%A1c/poem-NfZYXHHzcTanx5wu9YCHjw">Trừ dạ Trường An tác - 除夜長安作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-C%E1%BA%A3nh/author-nRcey3owAPDUSV_r8lgAmg">Lý Cảnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
